  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\n\nIf the asset has not been enabled previously, when a transaction request in 1-1 chat is received, the value of this asset is zero (0 USD). \n\n#### Note\n\nIf enable this asset after receiving the request and **re-login** to Status, the value of the asset in 1-1 chat will be updated.\n\n#### Expected behavior\n\nRelevant value of an asset is shown when a transaction request is received.\n\n#### Actual behavior\n\n![ezgif com-resize (20)](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/67952253/90624475-4c92c100-e218-11ea-9cb3-1c3c0635e8c1.gif)\n\n\n### Reproduction\n\nUser 1:\n1.  Open Wallet view\n2. Three dots on the top right -> Manage assets\n3. Ð¡heck the box for AMB\n4. Start 1-1 chat with User 2\n5. Request transaction -> Choose AMB in the assets list -> Enter any amount (e.g. 50)\n6. Tap Request\n\nUser 2:\n1. Open 1-1 chat with User 1\n\n### Additional Information\n\n- Status version: Nightly 19/08",
